title: Greece stigmatised by European Parliament’s regional committee (European United Left - Nordic Green Left)
text: ( Source : European United Left - Nordic Green Left ) 19/10/ 2015 The European Parliament adopted during its plenary session in early October specific EU funding measures for Greece , with a view to facilitating the implementation of these funds
